<name2:Kohralplsan Forest>
<number:1>

parameters: ここにEDイラストを貼る

The girl walks uneasily through the forest. She
had never ventured this far from the village
before.

However, the girl had a purpose. That's why,
despite being scared, she continued forward.

The place the girl was taught about long ago...
Her destination must be here. But... is it really
here? The girl looks around uneasily.

Before she knew it────── it really appeared right
in front of her. It was incredibly large...
shining in gold... magnificent... a dragon...!
Sol started working as a waitress...
\n<Adventurer>Berry pie! Bring me some berry pie!

Working as a waitress, by the time most of the
customers were drunk, one of the adventurers
started caressing Sol's butt...

\n<Adventurer>Hey Sol-chan... how about having a little fun
with me?

\n<Sol>N-No, you can't do that! Don't touch me like
that! I'll get angry, you know!

\n<Sol>Mmm... Well, I guess there's no helping it. Just
a little bit, okay?!

\n<Sol>Ah...nnn...huh... I was kind of looking forward
to it...

\n<Sol>\py[10] Ugh...h...hurry... I've been waiting for
this, you know...

An auction hidden in a world of darkness untouched
by the light of justice. The eerie light
illuminates the nobles with wicked smiles. Their
insatiable, bloated desires can no longer be
satisfied by ordinary means.

And then, the host appears on stage. Next to them
is Sol, wearing a collar.

A magic spell to seal her abilities is engraved on
that collar, rendering Sol unable to transform
into a dragon, resist, or even defy her current
state.

\n<Kidnapper>Ladies and gentlemen of nobility, merchants, and
esteemed individuals! Tonight, we present to you
this young lady! She is none other than the 'Child
of the Golden Dragon'!

\n<Abductor>Although she currently takes on a human form,
this golden tail is the evidence that she is
indeed the Golden Dragon!

\n<Kidnapper>This existence, more valuable than an equal
weight of gold! For a night of enchantment with
this beautiful and rare girl, starting at 1000
gold coins, she can be yours!

\n<Person Snatcher>Now, now! How about it? Those interested, raise
your bags of gold coins!

The nobles eagerly raise their hands and state
their prices. The one who offers the highest price
will gain the right to embrace Sol. It's a
despicable sight, even the pigs would turn away
from it.

The night of desire progresses. What will become
of Sol's fate...
